在[[香港|香港]]，'''直幡'''是一種和平抗議的工具<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=25121|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-19|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304191050/https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=25121|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/zh/interactive/2020/09/11/world/asia/hong-kong-speech.html|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-19|archive-date=2021-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210311134550/https://www.nytimes.com/zh/interactive/2020/09/11/world/asia/hong-kong-speech.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:倒梁2013-07-18g.JPG|thumb]]
漢字傳統上是垂直書寫及從上到下閱讀。[[香港|香港]]一直都有用大大小小的直幡。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Dewolf|first=Christopher|date=2018-08-08|title=1967: When the Bank of China Building Became a Giant Propaganda Machine|url=https://zolimacitymag.com/1967-when-the-bank-of-china-building-became-a-giant-propaganda-machine/|access-date=2020-09-29|website=Zolima City Magazine|language=en-GB|archive-date=2019-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190723141958/https://zolimacitymag.com/1967-when-the-bank-of-china-building-became-a-giant-propaganda-machine/|dead-url=no}}</ref>  較小的直幡有時會被用作選舉活動的材料或廣告。 人們可能還會偶爾看到直幡作為慶祝裝飾掛在路燈上。

[[File:香港大遊行追究中國六四屠城責任_2010_Hong_Kong_Protest_Demanding_China's_Accountability_for_June_4th_Massacre.jpg|thumb]]
在香港的大規模抗議和示威遊行中，香港示威遊行者會打平舉起長長的直幡<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.chinafile.com/conversation/hong-kong-protest|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210317191638/https://www.chinafile.com/conversation/hong-kong-protest|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbsnews.com/news/hong-kong-protests-1-7-million-protesters-march-victoria-park-latest-updates-today-2019-08-18/|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210313165710/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/hong-kong-protests-1-7-million-protesters-march-victoria-park-latest-updates-today-2019-08-18/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這些垂直幡標語大多是用[[廣東話|廣東話]]和[[繁體中文|繁體中文]]所寫，但有時作者會用[[簡體中文|簡體中文]]表達貶義和對[[共產黨|共產黨]]的不滿<ref>{{Cite news|date=2011-06-16|title=Taiwan deletes simplified Chinese from official sites|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-pacific-13795301|access-date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2021-03-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210325191123/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-pacific-13795301|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2018-06-22|title=Traditional or simplified Chinese? What’s behind a war of words|url=https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/short-reads/article/2151818/traditional-or-simplified-chinese-script-issue|access-date=2020-09-28|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203103021/https://www.scmp.com/magazines/post-magazine/short-reads/article/2151818/traditional-or-simplified-chinese-script-issue|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

自1989年以來在香港的[[天安門|天安門]]紀念遊行和活動中都會出現直幡<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/tiananmen-12172013160412.html|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324091847/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/china/tiananmen-12172013160412.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://time.com/5600355/tiananmen-massacre-30-anniversary/|title=存档副本|access-date=2020-12-25|archive-date=2020-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201206015648/https://time.com/5600355/tiananmen-massacre-30-anniversary/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但2014年的[[雨傘運動|雨傘運動]]標誌著香港山頭直幡運動的開始。<ref>{{Cite book|last=吳海傑， 王迪安|first=|title=香港動盪: 法與治的歷史與文化解讀|publisher=Hong Kong University Press|year=2020|isbn=9888528300|location=Hong Kong|pages=178}}</ref> 2014年的雨傘運動中，一群香港的攀岩人決定在獅子山上掛一幅30米長黃色直幡，並記錄在YouTube上。 當時有些香港市民都認為這是個玩笑<ref>{{Cite book|last=盧|first=峯|title=悼我城: 香港，你究竟失去了什麼？|publisher=亮光文化|year=2015|isbn=9888365088|location=香港|pages=160}}</ref>。自那天以來，香港各地出現了更多的山頂直幡，和平地表達對香港政府及中國政權的不滿。<ref>{{Cite web|title=清走黃色直幡 清不走人心|url=http://news.memehk.com/posts/%E6%B8%85%E8%B5%B0%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B4%E5%B9%A1%20%20%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83|access-date=2020-09-27|website=news.memehk.com|language=en|archive-date=2016-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160907143342/http://news.memehk.com/posts/%E6%B8%85%E8%B5%B0%E9%BB%83%E8%89%B2%E7%9B%B4%E5%B9%A1%20%20%E6%B8%85%E4%B8%8D%E8%B5%B0%E4%BA%BA%E5%BF%83|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 雨傘運動之前 ==

=== 1989年天安門廣場大屠殺 ===
{{main article|六四事件}}
[[File:Março_para_20º_anniversaio_de_Massacre_de_4_de_Junho_em_Hong_Kong.JPG|thumb]]
[[File:HKU_香港大學_Campus_太古橋_Swire_bridge_6-4_white_words_Oct-2011_Ip4_star.jpg|thumb]]

1989年6月4日，大屠殺發生後，[[香港大學|香港大學]]的學生們在[[香港大學|香港大學]]太古橋的黑色直幡，並用白色塗上一句「冷血屠城烈士英魂不朽 誓殲豺狼民主星火不滅」以表示對民主的支持並譴責中國政府<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hong Kong U 29層白油記憶 {{!}} 一悠|url=https://www.hkcnews.com/article/12529/六四29周年-香港大學-太古橋-12530/hong-kong-u-29層白油記憶|access-date=2020-09-30|website=眾新聞|language=zh|archive-date=2021-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210712015650/https://www.hkcnews.com/article/12529/%E5%85%AD%E5%9B%9B29%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8-%E5%A4%AA%E5%8F%A4%E6%A9%8B-12530/hong-kong-u-29%E5%B1%A4%E7%99%BD%E6%B2%B9%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管黑色的直幡僅懸掛了一天，但從布織物上滲過底並留在橋上的白色油漆成為直幡存在的歷史產物。此後，香港大學的學生每年直接重新將白色油漆在粉刷這二十個單詞<ref>{{Cite web|title=當年港大校園留下標語 舊生重返太古橋 證薪火不滅|url=https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20140605/AQTBS625MKVTKMBI2VP7KZ774E/|access-date=2020-09-30|website=Apple Daily 蘋果日報|language=zh-hk|archive-date=2021-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210621163410/https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20140605/AQTBS625MKVTKMBI2VP7KZ774E/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這可能是香港第一幅抗議直幡。隨著時間的流逝，香港每年的6月4日總會在晚上在[[維多利亞公園|維多利亞公園]]舉行紀念晚會。6月4日之前的周末，或者如果6月4日在周末，便會有大規模的遊行集會。 2020年，香港當局首次以健康為由拒絕了這一守夜，後來又以非法聚會而逮捕了許多人<ref>{{Cite web|title=Hong Kong: Tiananmen vigil crackdown another cynical attempt to curb peaceful dissent|url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2020/06/hong-kong-tiananmen-vigil-crackdown-another-cynical-attempt-to-curb-peaceful-dissent/|access-date=2020-09-29|website=www.amnesty.org|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201013095126/https://www.amnesty.org/en/latest/news/2020/06/hong-kong-tiananmen-vigil-crackdown-another-cynical-attempt-to-curb-peaceful-dissent/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-07|title=HK activists among 24 charged for Tiananmen vigil|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-53689265|access-date=2020-09-29|archive-date=2021-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210101125502/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-53689265|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2007 皇后碼頭保育運動  ===
{{main article|保留皇后碼頭事件}}
[[File:QP_protest_banners.jpg|thumb]]
數百名香港市民嘗試阻止香港政府對[[英國|英國]]殖民遺跡[[皇后碼頭|皇后碼頭]]的拆除。 除了絕食持續數天，抗爭者爬上碼頭頂部上懸掛四幅白色的直幡<ref>{{Cite web|title=P H Yang Photography {{!}} Queen's Pier - People's Power - 1 Jul 07|url=http://phyang.org/photo/queens_pier.htm|access-date=2020-09-27|website=phyang.org|archive-date=2013-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005142701/http://phyang.org/photo/queens_pier.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。直幡寫了「差你一個」，「保衛皇后」，「同佢死過」，「官逼民反」<ref>{{Cite web|date=2017-08-06|title=In Pictures: Demonstrations and demolition - 10 years since the Queen's Pier was pulled down|url=https://hongkongfp.com/2017/08/06/pictures-demonstrations-demolition-10-years-since-queens-pier-pulled/|access-date=2020-09-27|website=Hong Kong Free Press HKFP|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210114171908/https://hongkongfp.com/2017/08/06/pictures-demonstrations-demolition-10-years-since-queens-pier-pulled/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這項保存運動被認為是香港本地運動的誕生，因為年輕的香港市民更多地將自己視為獨立的香港人<ref>{{Cite web|date=2016-05-31|title=Queen’s Pier rebuilding plans anger protesters who fought its demolition|url=https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/1959472/queens-pier-rebuilding-plans-anger-protesters-who-fought-its-demolition|access-date=2020-09-27|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304191217/https://www.scmp.com/lifestyle/article/1959472/queens-pier-rebuilding-plans-anger-protesters-who-fought-its-demolition|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2007 香港中文大學畢業典禮 ===
2007年12月6日，在[[香港中文大學|香港中文大學]]大樓的頂層掛了一對直幡，寫了「[[董建華|董建華]]禍港殃民有博士 [[劉遵義|劉遵義]]求榮賣校無良知」，抗議當時的[[香港行政長官|香港行政長官]][[董建華|董建華]]被中大校長[[劉遵義|劉遵義]]授予[[榮譽博士|榮譽博士]]學位。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://hd.stheadline.com/news/topic.asp?contid=87 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-12-15 |archive-date=2020-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200826130732/https://hd.stheadline.com/news/topic.asp?contid=87 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=歷史時空的局限 {{!}} Y.t. Chan {{!}} 立場新聞|url=https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%99%82%E7%A9%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90/|access-date=2020-12-13|website=立場新聞 Stand News|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125053900/https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E6%99%82%E7%A9%BA%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%80%E9%99%90/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 2014年新界東北發展抗議 ===
{{main article|新界東北發展計劃}}

原居民和環保團體抗議政府缺乏與新界東北原居民的協商，以及在這項新的住房開發提案中缺乏香港生態和文化保護的抗議。 此外，[[香港特別行政區立法會|立法會]]預算委員會在未遵循適當程序的情況下通過了預算提案， 引起了數千香港居民的憤怒<ref>{{Cite web|date=2014-06-07|title=Protesters storm Legco over northeastern New Territories plan|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1526945/protesters-storm-legco-over-northeastern-new-territories-plan|access-date=2020-09-28|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2020-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223112305/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1526945/protesters-storm-legco-over-northeastern-new-territories-plan|dead-url=no}}</ref>。原居民張貴財和社運人士周諾恆兩個爬上人行天橋頂部懸掛四幅直幡，直幡上面懸掛著50,000個紅色的簽名<ref>{{Cite web|title=反建制壟斷 坪輋村民張貴財：唔做就冇機會贏！ {{!}} 獨媒報導|url=https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1038954|access-date=2020-09-28|website=香港獨立媒體網|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304191256/https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1038954|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 後來張貴財因不遵守行政命令而被罰款一千港元，而且可能是第一位因掛直幡而被罰款的香港市民<ref>{{Cite web|title=立法會外掛直幡反東北 張貴財周諾恒各罰款1000元 {{!}} 獨媒報導|url=https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1034890|access-date=2020-09-28|website=香港獨立媒體網|archive-date=2019-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424183144/http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1034890|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 2014年9月22日，大學罷課 ===
[[File:CUHK_Opposition_20140922.jpg|thumb]]

為表達對北京人大在8月31日决定的不滿，超過13,000名大學生聚集在香港[[中文大學|中文大學]]罷課，要求普選和民主<ref>{{Cite web|last=岑逸飛-論盡中港台|title=香港學生罷課運動的反思 {{!}} 岑逸飛-論盡中港台|url=http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/internationalaffairs/culture/27685|access-date=2020-09-28|website=ET Net|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304191300/http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/lifestyle/internationalaffairs/culture/27685|dead-url=no}}</ref>。其他要求包括，社會不平等加劇，增加政府透明度和官員的責任感<ref>{{Cite web|title=學聯：萬三人聚中大撐罷課 (16:35) - 20140922 - 港聞|url=https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20140922/s00001/1411375038333/%e5%ad%b8%e8%81%af-%e8%90%ac%e4%b8%89%e4%ba%ba%e8%81%9a%e4%b8%ad%e5%a4%a7%e6%92%90%e7%bd%b7%e8%aa%b2|access-date=2020-09-28|website=明報新聞網 - 即時新聞 instant news|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2021-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210622181515/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20140922/s00001/1411375038333/%E5%AD%B8%E8%81%AF-%E8%90%AC%E4%B8%89%E4%BA%BA%E8%81%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E6%92%90%E7%BD%B7%E8%AA%B2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=2014-09-22|title=Thousands of HK students at boycott|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-29306128|access-date=2020-09-28|archive-date=2015-01-19|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Vh2TAj4j?url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-29306128|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這次學生罷課得到了大學教授的支持，但香港政府繼續無視他們的要求，三個星期後是次罷課將演變成2014年的[[雨傘運動|雨傘運動]]<ref>{{Cite web|last=NormileSep. 15|first=Dennis|last2=2014|last3=Pm|first3=12:45|date=2014-09-15|title=Hong Kong academics support looming student strike|url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2014/09/hong-kong-academics-support-looming-student-strike|access-date=2020-09-28|website=Science {{!}} AAAS|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210508045357/https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2014/09/hong-kong-academics-support-looming-student-strike|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年9月22日香港中文大學的中庭垂直懸掛著兩幅黑色直幡:「抗命捉緊命運 罷課事在必行」<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jawicks75|date=2014-09-28|title=Transnational / Cinema / Reflections: Hong Kong Student Protest Banners: "Strike or Nothing"|url=http://jawicks75.blogspot.com/2014/09/hong-kong-student-protest-banners.html|access-date=2020-09-29|website=Transnational / Cinema / Reflections}}</ref>。在香港中文大學的抗議場地上看到的兩幅黑色和一幅紅色用白色油漆寫成的直幡：「傳人本之道」「授民主基業」「解末來之惑」<ref>{{Cite web|last=B|first=About The Author David|last2=Project|first2=urski David is co-director of the China Media|last3=Village|first3=editor of the project’s website He is the author of Dragons in Diamond|last4=Urbanisation|first4=A. Book of Reportage About|last5=China|first5=social activism in|last6=Times|first6=co-editor of Investigative Journalism in China His writings have appeared in the New York|last7=Review|first7=the Far Eastern Economic|last8=Journal|first8=the Wall Street|last9=Censorship|first9=Index on|date=2014-09-23|title=Posts on Hong Kong student boycott deleted|url=https://chinamediaproject.org/2014/09/23/posts-on-hong-kong-student-boycott-deleted/|access-date=2020-09-29|website=China Media Project|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023114625/https://chinamediaproject.org/2014/09/23/posts-on-hong-kong-student-boycott-deleted/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

