== 後雨傘時期 ==
[[雨傘運動|雨傘運動]]結束後，許多香港市民感到失落。 許多被當時社會認為的激進分子亦因暴動罪而被捕入獄<ref>{{Cite news|date=2015-08-27|title=HK student protest leaders charged|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-34070695|access-date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108204537/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-34070695|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年的旺角“魚丸革命”，標誌著港市民在民主和真普選之路爭取了近20年<ref>{{Cite news|date=2016-02-09|title=What happened in Mong Kok?|language=en-GB|work=BBC News|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-35529785|access-date=2020-09-27|archive-date=2021-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210321102703/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-35529785|dead-url=no}}</ref>。中國和香港政府更取消多位民選立法會議員的資格<ref>{{Cite web|date=2017-07-18|title='I won't give up fighting': barred Hong Kong politician pushes back against Beijing|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jul/18/i-wont-give-up-fighting-barred-hong-kong-politician-pushes-back-against-beijing|access-date=2020-09-27|website=the Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109013246/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2017/jul/18/i-wont-give-up-fighting-barred-hong-kong-politician-pushes-back-against-beijing|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 每年參加“六四”天安門紀念活動的年輕人亦越來越少。<ref>{{Cite web|date=2018-06-04|title=Despite student snub, attendance at June 4 vigil ‘higher than last year’|url=https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2149203/tiananmen-anniversary-vigil-hong-kong-hundreds-arrive|access-date=2020-09-27|website=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206073834/https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/2149203/tiananmen-anniversary-vigil-hong-kong-hundreds-arrive|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Hong Kong Remembers June 4, 1989 Tiananmen Massacre|url=https://time.com/4800835/tiananmen-june-4-hong-kong-vigil-china/|access-date=2020-09-27|website=Time|archive-date=2021-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118124608/https://time.com/4800835/tiananmen-june-4-hong-kong-vigil-china/|dead-url=no}}</ref>  然而，山頂的直幡懸掛活動仍然繼續。 

